actice purposes only and not for a numerical grade  students may help one another  get tutorial help  or even access the answers online   Cadet Faculty Responsibility on Work for Grade Click here for Modern Language Dept  policies on work for Grade  Modern Language Department policy stipulates that a cadet may leave the classroom during class ONLY in cases of emergency  Students who come to class unprepared and or without the text used for that day will be asked to leave resulting in a grade of zero for that day  Some Cuban links  W L Cuba page   U S  State Department s Cuba page   Cuban Interests Section in Washington  D C    Institute for Cuban and Cuban American Studies at the University of Miami   Cuba megalinks    Virtual walking tours of Cuba   Study abroad opportunities in Cuba   More study abroad opportunities in Cuba   CCCS Cuba links   Insight Programs   Cubaweb   AfroCubaweb   AfroCubaweb s links   Center for Cuban Studies in New York   Center for Cuban Studies Links   Cubanueva   Osvaldo Salas   El Comandante Che   La pagina de Ernesto Che Guevara   U S  Blockade information   UT Lanic s Cuba links   Cuba Free Press and their discussion forum   Cubanet    History Will Absolve Me  in English   Think Quest page on Cuban history   Motivational billboards   Biographies of primary revolutionaries  Who can visit Cuba  How to apply for a license to travel to Cuba Music links    Dictionary of Cuban music   Ernesto Lecuona   Celia Cruz   Buena Vista Social Club   Arturo Sandoval   Los Van Van   NG La Banda   Enrique Jorrin   Col  Bulger Barnett Home Courses VMI Spanish Drills Links of Interest Applications   Forms Language Skills      SP 316   Topics In Spanish Cuba Libre  Spring 2001 Instructor  Colonel Bulger Barnett Telephone  464 7457 Office  428 Scott Shipp Hall Office hours  Please email for appointment Email  Bulger BarnettKD vmi edu   Course description  Spanish 316 is designed to introduce the post intermediate student to issues of Cuban interest  Studen